title: Lands in industrial zone (I) occupied by existing slums/structures under renewal shall be allowed to be developed in accordance with the provisions contained in this sub-regulation 33(10) (A) and 33 (9) (A)
clause_text: Lands in industrial zone (I) occupied by existing slums/structures under renewal shall be allowed to be developed in accordance with the provisions contained in this sub-regulation 33(10) (A) and 33 (9) (A).
